user_instruction: 'Send an update to Sarah (sarah@alumni.prestige.edu) about the new admissions cycle. You can check out my Notion for information.'

formatted_items.arguments:
{
  "to": ["sarah@alumni.prestige.edu"],
  "subject": "Update on Our Latest Admissions Cycle",
  "body": "Hi Sarah,

I hope you're doing well! I wanted to share a quick update on the new admissions cycle.

• We saw another healthy uptick in applications this year, reflecting growing interest in the university.
• Because of the larger pool, our acceptance rate tightened further, and we ultimately shaped a small but exceptional incoming class.
• Academic indicators remained very strong, and we continue to attract students from a wide range of backgrounds and more than sixty countries.

Altogether, it’s shaping up to be one of our most accomplished and diverse cohorts yet.

Let me know if you’d like any additional details or if there’s anything you’d like to share with the alumni network. Thanks for staying engaged with us!

Best regards,
[Your Name]
Admissions Office
Prestige University"
}
